            "summary": "The recipe Tuxedo Brownie Re-Make (Adapted From A Pampered Chef ) can be made <b>in about 45 minutes</b>. One serving contains <b>318 calories</b>, <b>5g of protein</b>, and <b>25g of fat</b>. This gluten free recipe serves 4 and costs <b>95 cents per serving</b>. Only a few people really liked this dessert. This recipe is liked by 1 foodies and cooks. If you have cream cheese, milk, semi-sweet chocolate, and a few other ingredients on hand, you can make it. This recipe is typical of American cuisine. It is brought to you by Foodista. With a spoonacular <b>score of 13%</b>, this dish is rather bad. Similar recipes include <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/quesadillas-the-pampered-chef-145449\">Quesadillas (The Pampered Chef)</a>, <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/pampered-chef-perfectly-creamy-cheesecake-131237\">Pampered Chef Perfectly Creamy Cheesecake</a>, and <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/garden-ranch-pizza-pampered-chef-111107\">Garden Ranch Pizza-Pampered Chef</a>.",
